##<id="intro"> Introduction

Redis for PCF v1.6 focuses on increased operability and compatibility with Ops Manager v1.8.  
As of v1.6, metrics are emitted via the Loggregator Firehose. Metrics help operators monitor service health and usage. 
New, enhanced logging provides a fine-grained history of service usage.

