## <a id="compatibility"></a>Compatibility [DELETE THIS SECTION BECAUSE COMPATIBILITY IS ON THE INDEX PAGE]

Redis for PCF v1.6 is not compatible with Ops Manager version 1.7 or earlier. 
Versions of Redis earlier than 1.5.17 will not work in Ops Manager 1.8, so it is recommended to upgrade to the latest Redis 1.5.x tile before upgrading to Ops Manager 1.8.

